snippet.title: PlayStation - Iwatobi Penguin Rocky & Hopper (1997)
snippet.description:
DESCRIPTION
Iwatobi Penguin Rocky & Hopper is a Miscellaneous game, developed by F2 Company and published by Nippon Rental, which was released in Japan in 1997.
